      "name": "Dennis Yatunin"
    },
    "body": "This PR puts `T_sfc` in the default cache and uses it to compute `vertical_diffusion_boundary_layer_tendency!` and `rrtmgp_model_tendency!`. The value of `T_sfc` is `29 * exp(-lat_sfc^2 / (2 * 26^2)) + 271`, where `lat_sfc` is the latitude of points on the surface in a spherical space and 0 degrees in a flat space.\r\n\r\nCloses #451 ",
